    <div class="tn-note">
      <strong>&#x1f4dd; Cultural Note:</strong> The author is saying **all of the people** as a generalization for emphasis. If it would be clearer in your language, you could express the emphasis in a different way. Alternate translation: [an assembly of the people]
    </div>
    <div class="tn-note">
      <strong>&#x1f4dd; Cultural Note:</strong> The author is making a comment about what happened after the story as a result of the events within the story itself. This signals the end of the story. Use a natural form in your language for expressing the conclusion of a story.
